---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services & Pricing | Cascade Creatives" active="services">

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label animate-in">Services</p>
    <h1 class="animate-in delay-1">A better website.<br /><em>More customers.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub animate-in delay-2">We build websites that show up in search, look professional on every device, and make it easy for people to contact you. We also shoot the photos and videos that go on them.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Who it's for -->
<section class="reveal" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="who-strip">
      <p>We work with <strong>local service businesses, contractors, healthcare providers, and small companies</strong> across Whatcom and Skagit County &mdash; Bellingham, Ferndale, Lynden, Mt. Vernon, Burlington, Anacortes, and surrounding areas.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container">
  <!-- Web Design -->
  <div class="service-block reveal">
    <p class="service-num">01</p>
    <h2>Website Design &amp; <em>Redesign</em></h2>
    <div class="service-price">Starting at $1,200</div>
    <p>Whether you need a brand new website or your current one needs a complete overhaul, we build it from scratch &mdash; no templates, no page builders. Every site is custom-designed, loads fast, looks great on phones, and is built to show up in Google.</p>
    <p>Most businesses invest <strong>$1,500&ndash;$3,000</strong> depending on the number of pages and complexity. Sites typically launch in <strong>2&ndash;3 weeks</strong>.</p>
    <p class="service-includes"><strong>What&rsquo;s Included:</strong> <span>Custom design &middot; Mobile-friendly &middot; Google-ready (SEO) &middot; Contact forms &middot; Fast loading &middot; Hosting setup &middot; Post-launch support</span></p>
    <p class="service-maintenance">Optional: <strong>$75&ndash;$125/mo</strong> ongoing maintenance &mdash; updates, security, changes whenever you need them. Just text or call.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Quote &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Content Production -->
  <div class="service-block reveal">
    <p class="service-num">02</p>
    <h2>Photos, Video &amp; <em>Drone</em></h2>
    <div class="service-price">Starting at $500</div>
    <p>Your website is only as good as what&rsquo;s on it. We shoot professional photos, video, and aerial drone footage &mdash; formatted for your website, Google Business Profile, social media, and ads. Already have content? We&rsquo;ll integrate it.</p>
    <p>Over a decade of production experience. FAA Part 107 licensed for drone operations.</p>
    <p class="service-includes"><strong>What We Shoot:</strong> <span>Business photos &middot; Team and headshots &middot; Product/service video &middot; Social media reels &middot; Aerial drone footage &middot; Google Business photos</span></p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Shoot &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Strategy -->
  <div class="service-block reveal">
    <p class="service-num">03</p>
    <h2>Digital Strategy &amp; <em>Consulting</em></h2>
    <div class="service-price">Custom pricing</div>
    <p>Not sure what you need? We&rsquo;ll review your online presence &mdash; website, Google listing, social media, reviews &mdash; and tell you exactly where to focus. No fluff. Just a clear roadmap for getting more customers online.</p>
    <p class="service-includes"><strong>What This Covers:</strong> <span>Website audit &middot; Google Business optimization &middot; Social media review &middot; Content recommendations &middot; Growth roadmap</span></p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Let&rsquo;s Talk &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Quick contact strip -->
<section class="reveal">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px">Prefer to just talk?</p>
    <a href="tel:3603186052" class="phone-link">(360) 318-6052</a>
    <p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.85rem;margin-top:8px">Call or text anytime</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Not sure what you <em>need?</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Tell us what you&rsquo;re working on. We&rsquo;ll come back with a clear plan, an honest price, and a timeline you can hold us to.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .who-strip {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .who-strip p {
    font-size: .95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .who-strip strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .service-price {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(200, 255, 0, .06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 255, 0, .15);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .service-maintenance {
    font-size: .88rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  }
  .service-maintenance strong {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .phone-link {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #fff !important;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color .25s;
  }
  .phone-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent) !important;
  }
</style>
